data.description: Welcome to 2739 S. Beulah St!! A beautiful well kept move in home right in the Stadium District in South Philly! Upon entering the home you have a beautiful custom arched bricked porch, giving a tuscan villa feel,  a legit oasis of a porch front! Enter the home you will see an open living and dining area with hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen has granite countertops, wood cabinets with tiled backsplash and black modern appliances. Walk out to the large trex deck that has great space for BBQ and Patio, enjoy the sporting games and concerts from your deck! Walk to the basement you will find a fully finished basement can be used as another living area or perfect for storage. There is also a half bathroom down there for convenience. The 2nd floor features 3 bedrooms and a nice sized tiled bathroom! Talk about location, this home is nestled on quiet street with on street parking, just a rock throw away from the Sporting Complexes, Philly Live Casino, Shopping Centers and much more! Also easy access to all bridges and transportation! Come check out all this home has to offer!
